					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"水引", "Mizuhiki"},
					"“Oh, we’ll handle Tachibana all right. Bwahaha! We’ll serve him a full course of experiences, Seiran Island-style!”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"水引"},
					"“橘君的事放心交给我们来安排⋯⋯呵呵呵，让我们来帮她们安排一场深具青蓝岛风格的约会行程──！”",
